  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1311">
<l>peṇṇiyalā rellārum kaṇṇiṟ potuvuṇpar </l>
<l>naṇṇēṉ parattaniṉ mārpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are given to prostitution all those who are born as womankind enjoy you with their eyes in an ordinary way. I will not embrace you.</l>
            </lg>
